headline: BAE Systems Wins $184M Deal to Produce Amphibious Combat Vehicles
summary: BAESY lands a $184 million U.S. Marine Corps contract to build more Amphibious Combat Vehicles, lifting total ACV-30 orders past 100.

headline: L3Harris Blasts Off With a $1 Billion Pentagon Payload
summary: A government investment in defense manufacturing capabilities has pushed L3Harris stock near all-time highs as the company restructures for growth.
